{"tid":1386343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解鎖新兵種  情報兵！","createTime":"2019-07-30T10:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T11:39:06.000Z","uid":246250,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c2e24de63f1c874caa34c63c7dbca9b6048dce7d","tid":1386343,"uid":246250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:21:51.000Z","msg":"首先，新兵種 &mdash; 情報兵並唔係一般嘅哨兵！<br />\n<br />\n情報兵係喺位於中前線，提供不同資訊俾前線手足，例如：狗隊位置、附近戰線情況、撤退路線等等⋯⋯ <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點係前線可以知道後面和理非嘅人數，解決元朗7點半撤退嘅溝通不足問題</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/McVWcj8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMcVWcj8.png&h=4a2f4636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過咁多次發夢經驗，發覺好多時候喺中前線係上唔到網，唔太清楚狀況係點。每一次都係返到屋企先知道其他地方戰線出咗事。<br />\n<br />\n希望情報兵可以spread開信訊俾前線（記得之前有post講過可以用細塊嘅白板黎作指示）<br />\n<br />\n其實之前都有類似嘅情報兵，但係一個人傳一個人，轉播速度太慢"},{"pid":"f9f359afc5eb6d0f5017aa0b279bfccae79731a1","tid":1386343,"uid":246250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:22:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"378c46a9f5547112111146b4c77ce7b0cfe3420d","tid":1386343,"uid":246250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:22:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bdaac129d3a60082eabac5332840b5272110f6f9","tid":1386343,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:23:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae3444795c35a07d706b838f0119e0c93e0c8ec7","tid":1386343,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:23:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fe616e79ab4665f7cbd698ebe797fc17c306c25f","tid":1386343,"uid":215505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f616ae5469c8cc4e8867d95287c0072d3f66f44c","tid":1386343,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike